In Hui et al. (2017), only the last effect is described and simulated for different parameters the orbital decay times for Fornax in CDM and in the FDM cases. They found that in FDM the orbital decay time is longer, and four of the five decay times simulated are bigger than 10Gyr\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
