Future CMB experiments, CMB S4, will be much more sensitive to the energy density of the ultra-light particles (Hložek et al. 2017). They will be capable of probe different imprints that ultra-light particles can leave in the CMB in the range of masses 10-32eV<m<10-23eV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
