However, at those scales these system are dominated by astrophysical process, making it difficult to disentangle the behaviour of DM from those processes. To obtain cosmological information from these measurements is a challenge. Some recent studies (Muñoz et al. 2020) forecast that the matter power spectrum can be measured from the global 21 cm HI signal for an experiment with parameters close to EDGES (Bowman et al. 2018), with a precision of O(10%)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
