As we already discussed, McConnachie (2012) measured half-light radii inferred from the densities of 36 Local Group dwarf spheroidals, and when compared with the bound on the half mass radius predicted for the FDM (180), obtained a mass around m∼10-22eV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
